reviewText: A perfectly good waste of film.  But, then again, it may have been shot with a GoPro.  The acting was absolutely among the worst I've ever seen.  Couldn't take more the 15 minutes of this 'film'.  If the total budget for Drug Lordz exceeded $1K, it went well over budget.  The trailer to this 'film' is all you need to watch to see what a complete waste it is.

I'm from the San Francisco Bay Area so I watch pretty much any movie, drama series, etc., centered on the Bay Area. This movie actually doesn't show much of the Bay that you could identify with. I understand that this is a low budget film but the acting could have been a little better. The plot was ok but you could figure it out midway through the film. I think an above average score of 3 out of 5 stars is appropriate.
